===============================================================================
                        STATS - Character Attributes
===============================================================================

Your character has seven primary stats that affect your abilities:

PRIMARY STATS
-------------
STR (Strength)
  - Increases melee damage
  - Affects carrying capacity (future)
  - Damage bonus: STR / 2

DEX (Dexterity)
  - Increases hit chance in combat
  - Hit bonus: DEX * 3 percentage points

AGI (Agility)
  - Makes you harder to hit
  - Defense: Reduces enemy hit chance by AGI * 2 percentage points

CON (Constitution)
  - Determines your maximum HP
  - Max HP = 10 + (CON * 5)
  - Higher CON means you can take more damage

INT (Intelligence)
  - Currently affects magical abilities (future)

WIS (Wisdom)
  - Currently affects magical abilities (future)

CHA (Charisma)
  - Currently affects social interactions (future)

DERIVED STATS
-------------
HP (Hit Points)
  - Your health - when it reaches 0, you die
  - Max HP is based on your CON stat
  - Regenerates slowly when not in combat

XP (Experience Points)
  - Gained by defeating monsters
  - Different monsters give different XP:
    * Rat: 5 XP
    * Spider: 10 XP
    * Snake: 15 XP
    * Wolf: 20 XP
    * Orc: 25 XP

LEVEL
  - Your overall power level
  - Currently for display (advancement system coming soon)

GOLD
  - Currency for buying items (shops coming soon)
  - Monsters may drop gold in the future

VIEWING YOUR STATS
------------------
  score     - Shows all stats, level, XP, gold, and equipment
  hp        - Quick view of just health and combat status

See also: help combat, help equipment, help score
===============================================================================
